Two investigators of paranormal rumors, the veteran Dr. Margaret Matheson (Sigourney Weaver) and her young assistant, Tom Buckley (Cillian Murphy). Simon Silver (Robert De Niro), a legendary blind psychic, reappears after an enigmatic absence of 30 years and become the greatest international challenge to both orthodox science and for professional skeptics. Tom starts to get intensely obsessed with Silver, whose power of attraction grows with each new manifestation of inexplicable events.
